        <Parent_String>columns by location or context [300001633], columns (architectural elements) [300001571], columns and column components [300052248], supporting and resisting elements [300078047], structural elements [300078048], structural elements and components for structural elements [300078046], architectural elements [300000885], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
